LSL.mode is a syntax coloring 'mode' for Coda and SubEthaEdit text editors for
Macintosh. This mode only works with Coda 1, and is not updated for Coda 2.

This mode was originally written by Mark Lentczner, and updated by
Solo Mornington.

You can find information about using external text editors for LSL here:

http://wiki.secondlife.com/wiki/LSL_Alternate_Editors#SubEthaEdit_.5BC.5D

What is LSL? Ask wikipedia: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linden_Scripting_Language
